sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Service as Model Registry Service<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OAuth as OAuth Proxy Container<br/>8443/TCP
    participant OSAuth as OpenShift OAuth Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant REST as REST Container<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant DB as PostgreSQL/MySQL<br/>5432/3306 TCP

    Note over User,DB: Flow 1: External User Access (OAuth Mode)

    User->>Router: GET /api/model_registry/v1alpha3/models<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Router->>Service: Forward (Edge TLS Termination)<br/>HTTPS 443→8443
    Service->>OAuth: HTTPS Request<br/>Bearer Token
    OAuth->>OSAuth: Validate Token<br/>HTTPS/TLS 1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount Auth
    OSAuth-->>OAuth: Token Valid + User Identity
    OAuth->>OAuth: Check RBAC<br/>User must have GET on service/{name}
    OAuth->>REST: HTTP Request (localhost)<br/>8080/TCP
    REST->>DB: Query ML Metadata<br/>PostgreSQL/MySQL<br/>TLS (optional)<br/>Username/Password
    DB-->>REST: Query Results
    REST-->>OAuth: JSON Response
    OAuth-->>Service: HTTPS Response
    Service-->>Router: Forward Response
    Router-->>User: JSON Response

    Note over User,DB: Flow 2: Internal Cluster Access (Non-OAuth Mode)

    participant Pod as Internal Pod
    participant SvcInternal as Model Registry Service<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant RESTInternal as REST Container<br/>8080/TCP HTTP

    Pod->>SvcInternal: GET /api/model_registry/v1alpha3/models<br/>HTTP (No Auth)
    SvcInternal->>RESTInternal: HTTP Request
    RESTInternal->>DB: Query ML Metadata<br/>Username/Password
    DB-->>RESTInternal: Query Results
    RESTInternal-->>SvcInternal: JSON Response
    SvcInternal-->>Pod: JSON Response

    Note over User,DB: Flow 3: Operator Reconciliation

    participant API as Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Controller as Controller Manager
    participant WHSvc as Webhook Service<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Controller->>API: Watch ModelRegistry CRs<br/>HTTPS/TLS 1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    API->>Controller: CR Created/Updated Event
    Controller->>API: Create Deployment<br/>Create Service, Route, RBAC
    API->>WHSvc: Validate ModelRegistry CR<br/>HTTPS/TLS<br/>Webhook Client Cert
    WHSvc-->>API: Validation Result
    API-->>Controller: Resources Created

    Note over User,DB: Flow 4: Metrics Collection

    participant Prom as Prometheus
    participant MetricsSvc as Metrics Service<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS

    Prom->>MetricsSvc: Scrape /metrics<br/>HTTPS/TLS<br/>Bearer Token (ServiceAccount)
    MetricsSvc-->>Prom: Operator Metrics
